{"type":"text","timestamp":1775851893463,"sessionID":"ses_286fb62eeffeu87dFyPsA5cDKA","part":{"id":"prt_d79055c320011EwxeJ4tIZCYB7","messageID":"msg_d79053d61001rPlIYD0kfwwvGp","sessionID":"ses_286fb62eeffeu87dFyPsA5cDKA","type":"text","text":"## Archive Summary: AR-013 — Redis 存储实现\n\n### Completed\n\n- `redisStore` struct with `cli`, `sessionPrefix`, `expiryIndexKey`, `lastActivityIndexKey`\n- Constants: `sessionKeyPrefix`, `sessionExpiryIndexKey`, `sessionLastActivityKey`\n- `makeRedisOptions()` parses `REDIS_ADDR` and `REDIS_PASSWORD` from environment\n- `Ping()` executes PING and expects \"PONG\" response\n- `GetSandboxBySessionID()` uses GET and returns `ErrNotFound` for `redis.Nil`\n- `Close()` calls `cli.Close()`\n- `StoreSandbox()` pipeline with SETNX, ZADD expiry, ZADD last_activity\n  - Validates nil sandbox → error \"sandbox is nil\"\n  - Validates zero ExpiresAt → error \"invalid expiry: ExpiresAt is zero\"\n  - Validates empty SessionID → error \"session ID is required\"\n- `UpdateSandbox()` uses SetXX (not SetNX), fails when key doesn't exist, does NOT modify ZSETs\n- `DeleteSandboxBySessionID()` pipeline with DEL and ZREM (both indices), handles non-existent gracefully\n- `ListExpiredSandboxes()` uses ZRANGEBYSCORE on session:expiry\n- `ListInactiveSandboxes()` uses ZRANGEBYSCORE on session:last_activity\n- List operations return `nil, nil` when limit <= 0\n- `loadSandboxesBySessionIDs()` uses MGet, skips orphan ZSET members gracefully\n- `UpdateSessionLastActivity()` verifies existence first via EXISTS, uses time.Now() for zero timestamp\n\n### Deferred\n\n- **Unit tests** (Phase 8) — `pkg/store/store_redis_test.go` not created","time":{"start":1775851893460,"end":1775851893460}}}
